N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 17 ยง 79.45 - Garbage or other refuse disposal restricted

State Regulations

No person shall place, discharge or deposit in any manner, garbage or any refuse in or upon any part of the airport, except at such places
and under such conditions as the airport operator from time to time may
prescribe. Notes
